{"title":"满路春光满路花","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"满路春光满路花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线在心中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔上海〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走路快如劲风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志气赛过长虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想红似太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话亮如洪钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线在心中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《工人歌谣选》〕\t公社颂\t〔四川〕何李尹、王季仕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鹰展翅蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲤鱼摆尾龙潭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民有了公社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骏马奔向平川。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自四川《通川日报》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔西安〕刘培森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满路春光满路花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满路社员催战马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满路水担满路歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满路笑脸似桃花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银水进田麦浪滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦香千里醉人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦海随着歌声笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金难买公社春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《西安日报》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光不等人\t  〔河南〕许天柏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉甩长鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马儿跑得欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜铃叮当响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥土往上翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手扶耧把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬鞭高声喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“得得，枣红马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥这样慢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光不等人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春播要提前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要不听话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋后把账算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收买机器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定把你撤换。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马蹄如敲鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚起黄烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉哈哈笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身是喜欢！\t布谷鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔河北永年〕布谷：社员停住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你听我诉："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉花五谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早种早出！社员：布谷布谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚来两步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺的谷苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早已出土！布谷：棉花五谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早出早锄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早早间苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抵加粪土！社员：布谷布谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看清楚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二遍已过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三遍正锄！布谷：我脸发烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脖子发粗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣传来迟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞往别处！社员：布谷布谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用忙碌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别处社员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早就动锄！\t挖水渠\t  〔浙江湖州〕李苏卿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖出水渠似银线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织成银网撒地面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银网党设计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银网社员编，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金网银网网粮棉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠党靠社不靠天。\t    月月红\t    〔江苏苏州〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗外一枝月月红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纺织姑娘亲手种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘种花有心意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月月成绩与它同。\t  花　儿\t  〔青海〕高秀云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心上的花儿是串子莲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱了一个生一千；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习文化心里亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心窝里种下花儿田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花儿田是幸福田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福花儿开心间；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席浇水花儿盛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越唱越多唱不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《青海湖》〕\t    我知道\t      王燕生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我抱风枪开隧道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风枪乐得蹦蹦跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是晃，又是摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推我肩膀直是笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风枪风枪好伙伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的心情我知道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火车很快要进山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你已听见汽笛叫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好伙伴呀笑呵笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的心情我知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过这层花岗岩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看见祖国在飞跃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《解放军文艺》〕\t宝葫芦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔甘肃张掖〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们修个大水库，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活像一个宝葫芦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装进去一湖清水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒出来万担金谷。（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周令钊　插图"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}